{"tid":2050594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又幾好笑 隔牆有耳：想寸港記阻PoPo執法  元秋攞架嚟丟 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-04T08:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T09:31:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1733e923873723e4ddd61b359a5d8076f6b196","tid":2050594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200604/R7Y5J6PPRSFX7VDK6OEXH25A2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200604%2FR7Y5J6PPRSFX7VDK6OEXH25A2U%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=bba0c69d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200604%2FR7Y5J6PPRSFX7VDK6OEXH25A2U%2F&h=fcc32aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200604/R7Y5J6PPRSFX7VDK6OEXH25A2U/</a><br />\n<br />\n又幾好笑<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：想寸港記阻PoPo執法 <br />\n元秋攞架嚟丟 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為掩飾警暴同推卸自己搞亂香港嘅責任，777、李家超同PK鄧連埋建制派，呢排成日將假記者同傳媒發放假消息等毫無證據嘅講法掛喺口邊，務求嘗試令大話講得多就令人以為係真。<br />\n<br />\n早幾日元秋蔣麗芸就喺社交媒體出post，貼咗兩張美國警民對峙相，仲理直氣壯問網民「為何美國示威現場不見記者站在中間？」擺明想寸香港嘅記者成日阻住PoPo執法，不過佢咁做不但幫唔到政府，反而好快俾網民突破盲腸恥笑佢，短短幾日有逾3,000人留言，問元秋有冇諗過，如果張相唔係記者企係中間影，咁係乜水影？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃藍網民留言混戰<br />\n<br />\n其實元秋轉載張相，警察同示威者企咗喺左右兩邊，好快網民就突破盲腸留言反問：「呢張相係邊個影？你答我！」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。有網民恥笑「張相好明顯係記者企喺中間影，你唔係蠢到𠵱家仲未明呀」、「推到蔣麗芸諗吓自己講咗乜」，仲有人留言揶揄抽水，話「張相蒸出來㗎」、「梗係個警察用自拍棍影」，。。。。。。。。。。，結果變黃藍混戰。<br />\n<br />\n對攝影明顯有認識嘅網民，。。。。。。。。。。。，而張相正正係攝記主觀角度拍攝，當然見唔到自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n至於始作俑者元秋，佢最後就冇理大家解釋，唔知以佢智慧，係咪真係明白個答案呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XUALX5JAUREYRI6RTSHMF6WNVU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXUALX5JAUREYRI6RTSHMF6WNVU.gif&h=ab01a81e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"314110de73f7dc1d6cecd34324a83dea04aa3711","tid":2050594,"uid":55769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aygZLoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaygZLoB.jpg&h=d332c007&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82b8d7893e53cedd3ad235ba7e9b361993a765ea","tid":2050594,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"都係個句<br />\n建制派用得呢啲廢人<br />\n証明中國啲高層幾腐敗"}]}